A family from Igigo village in Budalang&rsquo;i sublocation, Bunyala subcounty, is all smiles after MP Ababu Namwamba gave a Sh45,000 bursary for their child to join Kolanya Boys&rsquo; High School in Teso. Allan Juma Bwire scored 366 marks in KCPE exam. His mother, Jentrix Auma, on Friday said she could not afford the fee and was happy to receive a cheque from the CDF manager.